# 📦 Mongoose CRUD API

A **Node.js** application using **Express.js** and **Mongoose** to perform full **CRUD** operations on MongoDB collections.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📋 Manage collections: **Todos**, **Cars**, **Books**, and **Restaurants**
- 🌐 RESTful API with full **JSON** support
- 🛠 Built with **Express.js** and **Mongoose**

---

## 📡 API Endpoints

### ✅ Todos

| Method | Endpoint           | Description       |
|--------|--------------------|-------------------|
| GET    | `/todos`           | Get all todos     |
| PUT    | `/todos/:id`       | Update a todo     |
| DELETE | `/todos/:id`       | Delete a todo     |

### 🚗 Cars

| Method | Endpoint           | Description       |
|--------|--------------------|-------------------|
| GET    | `/cars`            | Get all cars      |
| POST   | `/cars`            | Add a new car     |
| PUT    | `/cars/:id`        | Update a car      |
| DELETE | `/cars/:id`        | Delete a car      |

### 📚 Books

| Method | Endpoint           | Description       |
|--------|--------------------|-------------------|
| GET    | `/books`           | Get all books     |
| POST   | `/books`           | Add a new book    |
| PUT    | `/books/:id`       | Update a book     |
| DELETE | `/books/:id`       | Delete a book     |

### 🍽️ Restaurants

| Method | Endpoint              | Description           |
|--------|-----------------------|-----------------------|
| GET    | `/restaurants`        | Get all restaurants   |
| POST   | `/restaurants`        | Add a restaurant      |
| PUT    | `/restaurants/:id`    | Update a restaurant   |
| DELETE | `/restaurants/:id`    | Delete a restaurant   |

---

## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone <repo-url>

# 2. Install dependencies
npm install

# 3. Start the development server
npm run dev
```

